data.description: Introducing the perfect blend of comfort and style in this 4 bedroom, 2 and a half bath traditional 2 story home. This spacious haven is designed with your needs in mind! Freshly painted and ready to move in. The oversized master suite has a private bath, double vanity, 1 large walk-in closet, and THREE additional closets for all your storage needs.  This home also offers two extra storage spaces specifically dedicated to keeping your holiday decorations safe and sound.  The solid 1 hardwood bamboo flooring throughout the dining room and living room adds a touch of elegance and warmth to every gathering. For all you green thumbs out there, the raised garden beds are ready for you to bring your gardening dreams to life. They have mature blueberry bushes just waiting for you to pick their delectable fruits. Plus, perennial lilies adorn the front garden, adding bursts of color and beauty. To top it all off, enjoy a cozy breakfast area with new tile flooring!
